data.description: You'll Love this Home's Open Floor plan with Large Kitchen, a Living Room, Den, Dining Room and Huge Wrap-around Deck! It sits on a .73-acre lot in a nice neighborhood with underground utilities-enhancing views of the Carolina sky. Being towards the end of a cul-de-sac limits drive-by traffic. Having mature trees offers valuable shade and reduces mowing. The woods provide privacy and space to explore nature. There's a double concrete driveway and paved sidewalk to the front porch. Inside has vaulted ceilings, brushed nickel fixtures, tilt replacement windows and custom tilework in the bathroom. The roof was replaced in 2019. A Home Warranty is Available. The Owner Suite has a walk-in closet and ensuite with a shower and corner tub that still has the sticker on it. The Kitchen has plenty of cabinets, tile countertops, a spray faucet and an island with an eat-up bar. The den has a fireplace and sliding glass door that leads to a covered porch. Great Location near I-77 and Lake Norman!
